; Lima & Fernandes 2009 ; Gondim & Giacometti 2010 ;
Oliveira et al. 2010
;
Gondim et al. 2011
, 2013b ; Lopes 2011 ). In this study, we provide the first record of this species for Rio Grande do Norte . From depths of 0 to 50 m ( Tommasi 1966a ).
